name: Sterling Silver Dangling Flowers Earrings
description:
These exceptional earrings were made using handmade sterling silver ear wires and headpins and feature lovely teal glass flower beads and chocolate brown leaves.

Each earring measures 1.5 inches (3.8 cm) long.

These really are very pretty earrings.  

Note that I did not make the sterling silver findings.  I purchased them from an Artfire seller.  

***Free USPS first class shipping anywhere in the world.
